{{Taxobox | name = Mycobacterium phage packman | image_caption = | image = | virus_group = i | ordo = ''[[Caudovirales]]'' | familia = ''[[Siphoviridae]]'' | genus = ''[[L5likevirus]]'' | species = '''''Mycobacterium phage packman''''' }}
'''''Mycobacterium phage packman''''' is a [[bacteriophage]] known to infect bacterial species of the genus ''[[Mycobacterium]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://phagesdb.org/phages/PackMan/ |title=The Actinobacteriophage Database &#124; Phage PackMan |website=Phagesdb.org |date=2011-03-17 |accessdate=2017-04-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/G1BR88 |title=82 - Gp82 - Mycobacterium phage PackMan - 82 gene & protein |website=Uniprot.org |date= |accessdate=2017-04-27}}</ref> It is named after the famed arcade game character [[Pac-Man]], from the game of the same name.
